{"tid":1170482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】分析員：手機出貨量料跌1/4 最壞情況裁員千人","createTime":"2019-05-25T04:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T08:00:42.000Z","uid":54733,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0002fd869d039a4c055902e10d2356e15740a3b6","tid":1170482,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:34:38.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普封殺華為手機，「教訓」中國，外界已預期將影響華為的業績。市場研究公司Strategy Analytics的分析員預測，今年華為手機的出貨量將會減少24%，而明年會再跌23%；晶片行業分析員更指，在最壞情況華為可能要裁員1,000人，會從全球競爭者地位上消失。<br />\n<br />\n華為目前是全球第二大智能手機生產商，不過，Strategy Analytics認為華為失去Google軟件支援，又失去美國的晶片，只能用備用零件組裝，對消費者的信心將有重大影響，而且還要考慮後續維修問題，一旦維修時被換成中國自製的替換零件，將會打擊消費者的觀感。<br />\n<br />\nStrategy Analytics的分析員認為，華為手機沒有Google行動服務，將會為華為的業務造成巨大風險和不確定性。分析員認為，今年華為手機出貨量勢將減少，如果真的失去Google，明年可能會被擠出西歐的智慧型手機市場。<br />\n<br />\n總部位於上海的諮詢公司Intralink追蹤晶片行業的蘭德爾（Stewart Randall）則預期，華為可能需要裁員數千人，並在一段時間內，「從全球競爭者的地位上消失」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，華為副董事長胡厚崑在德國出席網絡安全會議時批評，華為受到「毫無依據的指控」和「非常不公的限制」，對華為在全球的數千家供應商和大量消費者帶來負面影響，有關的草率決定影響全球供應鏈，擾亂市場競爭，違背國際商業價值觀，開危險的先例。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音"},{"pid":"e95f2943c3a1bd3a58d05fce3b5e23005d1a75f2","tid":1170482,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:35:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190525/59639565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190525%2F59639565&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62CtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=fad3d57a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190525%2F59639565&h=6efd987b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190525/59639565</a>"},{"pid":"c4e9a52e2ab9613f1d16bae9d7b5565ef448e10d","tid":1170482,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出返d nokia3310 式電話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e350f2ca0ece8b148bed9a63502ca598866d0d","tid":1170482,"uid":159313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"1/4咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf91c0b5c321abd5c255334a89c15f6a1e644443","tid":1170482,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"華為又贏"},{"pid":"6bf279ec71381b1097df24c8b8954d2fdd46f7c3","tid":1170482,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c0e350f2ca0ece8b148bed9a63502ca598866d0d","tid":1170482,"uid":159313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"1/4咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"跌剩1/4 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcafc90a9e9e1c28c7e82f9230c7eec0436ccfb6","tid":1170482,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}